_:N96291d5ae574416fadca99766c6c1010 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alexandra Jones is Director General for Growth, Science and International at the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology (<abbr title=\"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\">DSIT</abbr>), appointed to the role in January 2026.</p>\n\n<p>Before this, Alexandra held the position of Director General for Science, Innovation and Growth at <abbr title=\"Department for Science, Innovation and Technology\">DSIT</abbr> from May 2023 to December 2025. Before that, she served as Director for Science, Research and Innovation at the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy (<abbr title=\"Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\">BEIS</abbr>) from April 2019 to May 2023, where she had also led the development of the 2017 Industrial Strategy white paper as Director of Industrial Strategy.</p>\n\n<p>Before joining <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\">BEIS</abbr>, Alexandra was Chief Executive of Centre for Cities, as well as being Chair of the London Stansted Cambridge Consortium and the Fast Growth Cities group, and a Commissioner on both London Finance Commissions and the Cardiff Capital Region Growth Commission. She has also held various director roles working on labour markets, economic development and public service reform.</p>\n\n" .
_:Nc46eb23ff4ab48e9a66290a28be6040c <http://schema.org/item> <https://www.gov.uk/> .
